{"tid":124881,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]純黑Choker(狗帶)係19世紀係妓女既象徵","createTime":"2017-02-18T04:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T03:18:59.000Z","uid":28469,"like":72,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11ad5835bdc09db1d1c0915b1d427e9c9bebe256","tid":124881,"uid":28469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:03:33.000Z","msg":"19世紀既法國妓女會帶上黑色狗帶企街話俾人知佢地係妓女揾緊生意 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1YEL60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1YEL60.jpg&h=5ca16c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以防有小學雞唔知咩係prostitution 呢個字姐係妓女 俗稱雞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQ8fG67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQ8fG67.jpg&h=162d9422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWiki講既Manet, Olympia, 1861<br />\n雖然上層社會都有帶choker作為裝飾 但係係好華麗有珠寶有鑽石<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/900H1im.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F900H1im.jpg&h=13fa473e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n得一張畫好似唔多夠說服力 黎多兩張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/115905_9dae0bc8fa52506dce4a78ebc4190a9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F115905_9dae0bc8fa52506dce4a78ebc4190a9a.jpg&h=55da2d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ekt94q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ekt94q.jpg&h=012ffcaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家可以見倒圖中既妓女都有帶黑色choker<br />\n最後送大家幾張港女帶狗帶做個比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/153EOCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F153EOCv.jpg&h=5f08e587&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6566w9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6566w9.jpg&h=be963488&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/120153_4a4a8a80e9e4b61527618ccd